<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13371</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于到了早上，阿拉丁穿着美丽的新衣服等待着他的伯父。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布到了以后，他们匆忙地走出了弯曲的街道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们今天去哪里，伯父？”阿拉丁问道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我今天会看到什么我以前从来没有看到的东西？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，我的孩子，你要有耐心。”马格里布回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45476</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会看到很多很棒的东西！令人惊讶的宝物！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>魔法师从来没有这么高兴过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是他一直等待的那一天！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67864</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一边笑一边拥抱阿拉丁——就像一个真正的伯父一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67865</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一堵又旧又高的城墙围着整个城市。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当那两个游客来到城墙边的时候，阿拉丁停住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我从来没有到过城墙的另一边去过。”他小声地说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你再往前一步就可以看到一个新的世界了。”马格里布拉着阿拉丁的手说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们一起穿过了城门，离开了城市。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们要在美丽的花园里面逛逛。”马格里布说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111012</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在每个地方，他们都能看到玫瑰花，清香的草药，果树和花的藤蔓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>闪闪发光的水从狮子的形状的喷泉里流出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看到这些景色你开心吗？”马格里布问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我以前从来没有看到过这些东西！”阿拉丁说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“每个东西都让我很开心！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的朋友们，阿拉丁很开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他也很饿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>跟他伯父走了太久，肚子都叫了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166106</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泽巴没有给他准备任何食物，他在想他要吃点什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他没有必要担心这个。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布从长袍里拿出了一个芝麻饼干和一些无花果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们坐在树下吃了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布还告诉了阿拉丁他在埃及的生活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一些故事是真的，有一些故事不是真的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193766</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是只过了一小会儿，魔法师就迫切地想继续走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快点儿。”他说，“最棒的还在后面呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们继续往前走——从一个花园到另一个花园——直到没有花园的地方。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁知道土地没有了芬芳，也没有了青绿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>土地被太阳晒成了棕色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>马格里布走得越来越快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁不得不跑着追他，他被滚烫的石头绊倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245611</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我好累啊，伯父！我可以休息一下吗？”他说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245612</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不行！”魔法师回答，“就是这条路，快点儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我们现在是去哪儿啊，伯父？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这里没有花园了，只有光秃秃的山丘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261458</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果很远的话，我不能继续走了，我们应该回去了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不会太远的。”马格里布回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很快，你会看到你可以想象到的最美的花园！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是他们所到达的不是一个花园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们来到了一个有很多岩石的高高的山丘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，阿拉丁，你可以坐下了。”魔法师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的眼睛像发光了一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们终于到了我在寻找的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312050</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁为能够休息感到高兴，但是他也很兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312051</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去找一些棍子来生火。”马格里布命令他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，伯父。”阿拉丁回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他立马站起来，然后把找到的树枝堆在了一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>335188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当火烧起来了，马格里布从他的袖子里拿出了一个银色的盒子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>335189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打开了盒子，拿出了一些闻起来很甜的粉末。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他说了一些阿拉丁听不懂的奇怪的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>346760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘是咒语吗？’阿拉丁心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>350791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>355716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后马格里布把粉末扔进了火里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>355717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>361021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在那时，天空变暗了，电闪雷鸣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>361022</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>367602</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大地剧烈地晃动起来，岩石从阿拉丁的四周落下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>367603</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>372267</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，大地在阿拉丁的面前裂开了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>372268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>380680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁尖叫了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>